# PMS - Property Management System (Opera PMS Alternative)

## Project Overview

Open-source Property Management System built as a modern Opera PMS alternative.
Stack: Fastify 5 + Next.js 15 + PostgreSQL + Drizzle ORM
MVP: Single hotel — Reservations, Front Desk, Housekeeping, Financial Core, Auth

## Communication

Always communicate in Russian. Technical terms stay in English.
User name: Oci

## Core Philosophy

**"Opera Logic, Modern Implementation"**
1. Study Opera DB for data relationships
2. Study Opera Help for business rules
3. Implement clean, modern code
4. Skip legacy complexity

## Project Structure

```
apps/api/src/routes/    — API endpoints (Fastify)
apps/web/src/app/       — Frontend pages (Next.js App Router)
packages/db/src/schema/ — Database schema (Drizzle ORM)
docs/                   — Project documentation
_bmad/                  — BMAD method agents and workflows
_bmad-output/           — Planning and implementation artifacts
```

## Development Commands

```bash
pnpm install
pnpm --filter @pms/api dev    # API on :3001
pnpm --filter @pms/web dev    # Web on :3000
pnpm --filter @pms/db db:push # Apply schema
pnpm --filter @pms/db db:seed # Seed data
```

